    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/e87ce73cab7b4d0cf796adffde063037.poster.avif?t=1764839838\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/e87ce73cab7b4d0cf796adffde063037.webm?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/e87ce73cab7b4d0cf796adffde063037.mp4?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With no gold of his own, Niblet sets off on a quest to collect treasure, grow stronger, and save his one and only companion. Run through bustling areas and face off against greedy rich foes, from a cunning merchant to a ruthless queen. The odds are stacked against him, but Niblet won't stop the rescue!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Maps, Levels, and Challenges</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Never the same run twice – with randomized maps, levels, and encounters, each playthrough offers a fresh challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/9137b52779c3a4a8eab51b6fe9759ef7.poster.avif?t=1764839838\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/9137b52779c3a4a8eab51b6fe9759ef7.webm?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/9137b52779c3a4a8eab51b6fe9759ef7.mp4?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Over 150+ Items </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategically manage your gold to purchase upgrades from the shop, for effects such as healing, increased movement speed, extra jumps, and even new abilities! Unlock secret items and content for every new game you play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/c4eb73f89d00f4bfb46e14af14ece9cb.poster.avif?t=1764839838\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/c4eb73f89d00f4bfb46e14af14ece9cb.webm?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/c4eb73f89d00f4bfb46e14af14ece9cb.mp4?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/0b28f2ad418757726ec2354ef6c52de7.avif?t=1764839838\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras_big/0b28f2ad418757726ec2354ef6c52de7.avif?t=1764839838 width=800 height=168 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Encounters &amp; Alternative Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looking for more than just loot and legwork? Experience the best of both worlds with roguelike progression, challenges, and randomized D&amp;D-style encounters. Every corner could bring a new twist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/e05039f74d9d28a38782406c10c85c05.poster.avif?t=1764839838\" width=800 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/e05039f74d9d28a38782406c10c85c05.webm?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/e05039f74d9d28a38782406c10c85c05.mp4?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2-Player Local Co-Op</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rescue does not have to be a solo mission! Grab a second controller, team up, combine your skills, share the gold, and double the chaos. Unlock new goblin characters with unique starting abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/2f65834ae41794046cf9b33dbaa302d7.poster.avif?t=1764839838\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/2f65834ae41794046cf9b33dbaa302d7.webm?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/2f65834ae41794046cf9b33dbaa302d7.mp4?t=1764839838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller Support (and recommended!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Boss fights, and rare difficult hidden ones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 Challenge Rooms &amp; Mini-games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A good boi</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras/ce2f1607571cc962e7b81dafa32417ed.avif?t=1764839838\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303630/extras_big/ce2f1607571cc962e7b81dafa32417ed.avif?t=1764839838 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
